data.description: ***THIS PROPERTY IS ELIGIBLE FOR THE COMMUNITY LENDING PROGRAM WHICH PROVIDES DISCOUNTS TO THE INTEREST RATES FOR PRIMARY RESIDENCE UP TO 1.5%*** Ideally situated at the top of a hill on a quiet cul-de-sac, this home boast great curb appeal with a nice and neatly landscaped low maintenance front yard with turf and PAID OFF solar. First floor features a spacious tiled entry, formal living room, large kitchen, family room, laundry room and half bath. Kitchen opens to a spacious family room and offers ample cabinet space, double ovens, 5 burner gas stove, island and barstool seating. Laundry room is equipped with a clean start rain soft water softening system specifically for the washer, as well as soft water throughout the house. 2 car garage with tankless water heater. Upstairs offers a loft, 2 large guest rooms with walk in closets and a guest bathroom with double sinks. The master retreat is truly unique! With it's own bedroom within a bedroom, your master retreat offers flex space perfect for an office, nursery, gym or hobby room! Great views span the entire backside of the home, and large windows in the master bedroom offer lots of natural light in addition to mountain and city views. Your master retreat also features a fully updated spa like ensuite complete with soaking tub, shower, custom tile counters, dual vanities and a large walk in closet. This gated community offers pool. playground and views throughout!
